  <h2><span id="Roles_|_Responsibilities"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Roles_.7C_Responsibilities">Roles | Responsibilities</span></h2>
  <p><b><span id="Change_Manager">Change Manager - Process Owner</span></b> </p>
  <ul>
    <li>The Change Manager controls the lifecycle of all Changes. His primary objective is to enable beneficial Changes to be made, with minimum disruption to IT services. For important Changes, the Change Manager will refer the authorization of Changes to the Change Advisory Board (CAB).</li>
  </ul>
