  <p><b>Remarks</b> </p>
  <p><span id="Accountable">[1] <i>A: Accountable</i> according to the RACI Model: Those who are ultimately accountable for the correct and thorough completion of the Change Evaluation process.</span> </p>
  <p><span id="Responsible">[2] <i>R: Responsible</i> according to the RACI Model: Those who do the work to achieve a task within Change Evaluation.</span> </p>
  <p><span id="Team">[3] In cooperation, as appropriate: Applications Analyst, Technical Analyst, Configuration Manager, Project Manager, Risk Manager and others. </span>&nbsp;</p>
